{"tid":1699111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"周同學既仇我地要記一世","createTime":"2019-11-08T02:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T03:01:41.000Z","uid":2526,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a50a4201c67d3ff5f4ee0fb1558dea4423f53cd3","tid":1699111,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"全部同我記住<br />\n周同學出事時，黑警講大話，話自己無入停車場，一定要煲大佢<br />\n10月1向學生心口開槍，我地要記一世<br />\n831，721 爆眼，全部都要記一世<br />\n仲有黨鐵出軌唔可以忘記！！！<br />\n仲有好多好多好多，大家一齊補充整張list<br />\n每日都要睇，每日都要煲！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警填命！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ef0ef9459e11f629caae216770c277455b3d2bd","tid":1699111,"uid":322261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"一定要"},{"pid":"f24eb95c028750e8e7d33bdb63b07cf2e3d521ec","tid":1699111,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"係外國發生嘅話<br />\n啲人今晚就走出嚟抗爭啦"},{"pid":"f3fc0d1f3e964db55f7221cc4a5bab35b879b3e1","tid":1699111,"uid":331949,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">次次都係咁講，然後呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n唔該喇，香港人，真係唔好善忘，睇下維吾爾，睇下西藏，台灣。<br />\n當ISIS都係中共funded嘅時候，了解下你對手係乜"},{"pid":"89967776d047e2a2ba76beb224753e36c1fb7fd3","tid":1699111,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"記記記<br />\n真係等你記成世又點<br />\n個政權無痛無癢"},{"pid":"234ea0c12d49a80ea707a65eb282be3ac85d27a4","tid":1699111,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c7bc748c79fef9d5c299cc7573dfad61a6717130","tid":1699111,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"喃嘸阿彌陀佛，一路好走"},{"pid":"1a4784e83e7f0efbeaa16920591de9752ae6cad1","tid":1699111,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89967776d047e2a2ba76beb224753e36c1fb7fd3","tid":1699111,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"記記記<br />\n真係等你記成世又點<br />\n個政權無痛無癢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"唔記啊？<br />\n咁忘記囉<br />\n連你都可以不痛不癢做中國人既奴隸"},{"pid":"81f4c6b422fb05df39d3b390d6aea8bb919f793e","tid":1699111,"uid":206284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"香港人！！ 還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係班狗直接或間接累死周手足<br />\n阻30分鐘呀！<br />\n今次係有手足隻身跑出去擋狗<br />\n如果唔係我地可能連周手足生定死都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多無比人見到 消失咗既手足&hellip;<br />\n有啲直播比狗打到昏迷失禁既手足&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n堅持呀！企出黎呀 ！<br />\n香港人 還拖呀！"},{"pid":"c02980aa4072bf08c43f84b73dd7ea49a99ab4b1","tid":1699111,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a4784e83e7f0efbeaa16920591de9752ae6cad1","tid":1699111,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89967776d047e2a2ba76beb224753e36c1fb7fd3","tid":1699111,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"記記記<br />\n真係等你記成世又點<br />\n個政權無痛無癢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"唔記啊？<br />\n咁忘記囉<br />\n連你都可以不痛不癢做中國人既奴隸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好咁大反應，ching嘅講法係我地記之餘要做得更多。"}]}